00:03:24.180 --> 00:03:26.300
and find somewhere you can be free.

00:03:28.720 --> 00:03:30.540
What is she trying to do?

00:03:41.550 --> 00:03:42.350
Yan,

00:03:42.950 --> 00:03:44.280
are you feeling unwell?

00:03:44.730 --> 00:03:45.490
I'm fine.

00:03:50.810 --> 00:03:52.940
I'll call the imperial doctor for you.

00:04:00.480 --> 00:04:02.210
It's good to have you by my side.

00:04:03.560 --> 00:04:04.980
I'll always be here.

00:04:26.480 --> 00:04:27.540
Don't worry.

00:04:27.920 --> 00:04:29.500
We've just gotten married.

00:04:31.270 --> 00:04:32.500
I wouldn't bear

00:04:32.700 --> 00:04:34.060
to leave you alone.

00:04:50.010 --> 00:04:50.810
Alright.

00:04:52.270 --> 00:04:53.750
I need to go out myself

00:04:53.770 --> 00:04:55.050
to find Miss Ruoyao.

00:04:55.640 --> 00:04:56.790
If we can't find her,

00:04:57.050 --> 00:04:58.650
not only will Brother go mad,

00:04:58.920 --> 00:04:59.930
but

00:05:00.220 --> 00:05:01.880
other troubles might follow.

00:05:02.030 --> 00:05:02.830
I'll go now.

00:05:04.580 --> 00:05:05.380
Yan,

00:05:07.460 --> 00:05:08.680
have you considered

00:05:09.280 --> 00:05:11.320
that Zhou Kui might not leave at all,

00:05:11.520 --> 00:05:13.100
but instead burn his bridges

00:05:13.100 --> 00:05:14.360
and fight to win or die?

00:05:16.090 --> 00:05:17.850
Do you know anything else?

00:05:19.790 --> 00:05:20.750
Do you know

00:05:22.420 --> 00:05:23.550
how His Majesty died

00:05:24.590 --> 00:05:26.140
in the previous life?

00:05:28.980 --> 00:05:30.840
In the 11th year of Xinshou reign,

00:05:31.000 --> 00:05:32.600
His Majesty fell gravely ill

00:05:33.540 --> 00:05:34.930
and when he was on his deathbed,

00:05:34.930 --> 00:05:37.190
he passed the throne to the Crown Prince.

00:05:37.220 --> 00:05:39.650
But His Majesty had always
been in good health.

00:05:39.650 --> 00:05:41.650
How could he suddenly become so ill?

00:05:42.140 --> 00:05:43.180
Are you saying

00:05:43.960 --> 00:05:45.890
Father was also killed by Zhou Kui?

00:05:46.520 --> 00:05:48.780
Although there's no concrete evidence,

00:05:48.890 --> 00:05:50.750
thinking about it carefully now,

00:05:52.300 --> 00:05:54.700
it could indeed
have been Zhou Kui's doing.

00:05:55.680 --> 00:05:56.720
At that time,

00:05:57.909 --> 00:05:59.120
I had already married Li Shu

00:05:59.120 --> 00:06:00.850
and became the Crown Princess.

00:06:02.120 --> 00:06:03.650
After His Majesty passed away,

00:06:03.650 --> 00:06:05.780
he left the throne to the Crown Prince.

00:06:06.050 --> 00:06:08.230
And I became the mistress
of the imperial harem.

00:06:08.230 --> 00:06:10.360
Zhou Kui used my position as Empress

00:06:10.360 --> 00:06:11.890
to throw his weight around.

00:06:15.200 --> 00:06:17.140
Plus, I saw Linglan

00:06:17.300 --> 00:06:19.960
secretly meeting with
someone from the palace.

00:06:20.570 --> 00:06:23.230
Zhou Kui must have planted spies
around His Majesty,

00:06:23.230 --> 00:06:25.360
otherwise he couldn't have done this.

00:06:27.320 --> 00:06:28.530
Then I'll go to the palace

00:06:28.530 --> 00:06:30.210
and warn Father to be more vigilant.

00:06:30.210 --> 00:06:30.970
Also,

00:06:30.990 --> 00:06:33.010
increase patrols inside the Imperial City.

00:06:33.010 --> 00:06:34.340
Post guards at the city gates.

00:06:34.340 --> 00:06:36.670
I feel Zhou Kui still
has some backup plan.

00:06:37.330 --> 00:06:38.390
I'll be going then.

00:06:49.790 --> 00:06:50.640
[I'm on the verge of being arrested.
Find a way to enter the palace.]

