[Use the servants' secret passage
or fake imperial orders.]

00:07:16.200 --> 00:07:17.240
Master,

00:07:17.260 --> 00:07:18.810
I have failed in my task.

00:07:18.840 --> 00:07:20.250
Please punish me.

00:07:21.240 --> 00:07:22.600
This mistake

00:07:23.370 --> 00:07:26.430
is beyond your power alone to rectify.

00:07:28.210 --> 00:07:29.410
Master,

00:07:29.440 --> 00:07:31.160
what should we do next?

00:07:34.100 --> 00:07:35.540
Proceed as planned.

00:07:35.570 --> 00:07:36.760
As for the rest,

00:07:36.790 --> 00:07:38.270
I

00:07:38.290 --> 00:07:39.450
have my ways.

00:07:40.330 --> 00:07:41.130
Yes.

00:07:47.909 --> 00:07:49.230
Master ordered

00:07:49.470 --> 00:07:50.620
to plant explosives

00:07:50.640 --> 00:07:51.840
in these locations.

00:07:53.630 --> 00:07:54.740
Act quickly.

00:07:55.050 --> 00:07:55.930
-Yes.
-Yes.

