His Majesty has just risen.

00:08:06.670 --> 00:08:08.460
Please wait in the side hall,
Your Highness.

00:08:08.460 --> 00:08:10.460
I will go and announce your arrival.

00:08:10.800 --> 00:08:11.760
You may go.

00:08:11.780 --> 00:08:12.540
Yes.

00:08:53.560 --> 00:08:54.640
Your Majesty,

00:08:55.340 --> 00:08:56.670
the person has arrived.

00:08:57.020 --> 00:08:58.340
Yan is here?

00:09:01.160 --> 00:09:01.760
I,

00:09:01.760 --> 00:09:02.720
Zhou Kui,

00:09:02.720 --> 00:09:03.780
pay my respects

00:09:03.810 --> 00:09:04.770
to Your Majesty.

00:09:24.760 --> 00:09:26.160
You actually conspired with an outsider

00:09:26.160 --> 00:09:27.320
to harm me?

00:09:28.040 --> 00:09:29.120
Outsider?

00:09:33.010 --> 00:09:34.410
Lord Zhou

00:09:34.440 --> 00:09:37.300
is my own brother.

00:09:38.920 --> 00:09:40.490
The chief steward by His Majesty's side

00:09:40.490 --> 00:09:42.530
is actually my father's brother.

00:09:42.600 --> 00:09:45.370
No wonder we could
enter the palace so easily.

00:09:58.560 --> 00:09:59.840
It's been so long.

00:09:59.930 --> 00:10:01.860
Why hasn't Father summoned me yet?

00:10:02.590 --> 00:10:03.720
Something's wrong.

00:10:05.810 --> 00:10:06.900
Your Highness,

00:10:06.920 --> 00:10:09.860
where are you going?

00:10:12.760 --> 00:10:15.670
[Crown Prince's Mansion]

00:10:41.170 --> 00:10:42.170
Crown Prince Shu.

00:10:42.710 --> 00:10:43.470
What is it?

00:10:43.650 --> 00:10:44.920
His Highness has been to the palace
for a long time

00:10:44.920 --> 00:10:46.320
and hasn't returned yet.

00:10:46.590 --> 00:10:47.860
I'm worried about him.

00:10:48.710 --> 00:10:50.210
I'll send someone to the palace right away

00:10:50.210 --> 00:10:51.570
to check on Yan.

00:10:52.740 --> 00:10:54.140
Thank you.

00:10:55.140 --> 00:10:56.230
Your Highness,

00:10:56.260 --> 00:10:57.060
Your Grace,

00:10:57.080 --> 00:10:59.600
I was patrolling the city as ordered

00:10:59.630 --> 00:11:01.160
and discovered something suspicious.

00:11:01.160 --> 00:11:01.960
What is it?

00:11:02.720 --> 00:11:03.600
Near the Imperial City,

00:11:03.600 --> 00:11:05.410
there seems to be the smell of gunpowder.

00:11:05.410 --> 00:11:06.910
I just sent someone to investigate

00:11:06.910 --> 00:11:09.170
and found traces of sulfur and charcoal.

00:11:09.800 --> 00:11:11.660
It's not the Fireworks Festival.

00:11:12.440 --> 00:11:14.720
Why would there be gunpowder and charcoal?

00:11:14.720 --> 00:11:16.250
Gunpowder and charcoal...

00:11:18.700 --> 00:11:19.760
Lieutenant Liang,

00:11:19.950 --> 00:11:20.950
are you certain?

00:11:22.090 --> 00:11:23.650
I smelled it clearly.

00:11:24.320 --> 00:11:26.650
My hometown is known
for gunpowder production.

00:11:26.650 --> 00:11:27.270
Since childhood,

00:11:27.270 --> 00:11:30.000
I grew up surrounded
by black powder and fire caltrops.

00:11:30.000 --> 00:11:31.730
Most people wouldn't notice this smell,

00:11:31.730 --> 00:11:33.530
but I recognize it immediately.

00:11:35.430 --> 00:11:36.490
Lieutenant Liang,

00:11:37.230 --> 00:11:39.030
I need you to do something for me.

00:11:50.100 --> 00:11:51.580
This dragon throne

00:11:52.200 --> 00:11:54.240
is truly magnificent.

00:12:04.250 --> 00:12:06.200
It's comfortable to sit on too.

00:12:07.000 --> 00:12:08.120
No wonder so many people

00:12:08.120 --> 00:12:09.320
fight desperately

00:12:09.320 --> 00:12:11.120
to sit on this throne.

00:12:11.960 --> 00:12:13.560
You've sat here long enough.

00:12:14.640 --> 00:12:15.600
Make way

00:12:15.820 --> 00:12:17.620
and let someone else have a turn.

00:12:24.230 --> 00:12:25.220
Zhou Kui,

00:12:25.650 --> 00:12:27.400
how dare you!

00:12:27.430 --> 00:12:29.510
A mere Minister of Rites

00:12:29.750 --> 00:12:31.750
with ambitions to usurp the throne.

00:12:32.260 --> 00:12:33.370
Usurp?

00:12:35.760 --> 00:12:37.080
The empire

00:12:37.680 --> 00:12:39.540
belongs to the virtuous.

00:12:39.570 --> 00:12:41.140
In both civil and military affairs,

00:12:41.140 --> 00:12:42.700
I can say without doubt

00:12:42.720 --> 00:12:44.100
that I'm second to none.

00:12:44.450 --> 00:12:45.970
Why shouldn't this empire

00:12:45.990 --> 00:12:47.390
be mine to rule?

00:12:47.920 --> 00:12:50.210
Not to mention that since 30 years ago,

00:12:50.240 --> 00:12:52.020
Yunrui should have been destroyed.

00:12:52.020 --> 00:12:54.000
This should have been mine all along!

00:12:54.000 --> 00:12:55.910
If you hadn't supported the Daqing rebels,

00:12:55.910 --> 00:12:58.460
how would I have ended up like this?

00:12:59.960 --> 00:13:00.960
You are...

00:13:05.220 --> 00:13:07.820
the Crown Prince
of the former Daqing dynasty?

00:13:11.680 --> 00:13:12.720
30 years.

00:13:12.930 --> 00:13:14.420
It has been 30 years.

00:13:14.870 --> 00:13:17.230
No one has addressed me that way.

00:13:17.790 --> 00:13:18.960
But the good thing is

00:13:19.810 --> 00:13:22.140
now I've returned to this court

00:13:22.160 --> 00:13:24.040
and sit on this dragon throne!

00:13:25.280 --> 00:13:26.560
Get off my throne now!

00:13:29.290 --> 00:13:31.550
You'd better understand the situation.

00:13:31.600 --> 00:13:32.640
Now

00:13:33.910 --> 00:13:35.110
it's not up to you.

00:13:40.530 --> 00:13:41.400
Zhou Kui,

00:13:41.600 --> 00:13:43.460
Yunrui has never mistreated you.

00:13:43.710 --> 00:13:45.150
I have treated you well.

00:13:45.180 --> 00:13:46.120
Why would you do this?

00:13:46.120 --> 00:13:47.440
Shut up!

00:13:49.320 --> 00:13:50.470
For you,

00:13:50.580 --> 00:13:51.940
titles and rewards

00:13:51.970 --> 00:13:53.810
are the greatest gifts!

00:13:53.830 --> 00:13:54.950
But for me...

00:13:54.980 --> 00:13:56.280
For me,

00:13:57.640 --> 00:13:59.480
I can't forget all these years

00:13:59.500 --> 00:14:02.740
of humiliation,
begging at your feet like a dog.

00:14:02.760 --> 00:14:04.090
I will avenge this shame

00:14:04.110 --> 00:14:05.510
and reclaim the throne!

00:14:07.160 --> 00:14:08.840
I want Yunrui's empire

00:14:08.860 --> 00:14:10.540
to exact my revenge.

00:14:11.170 --> 00:14:11.970
I

00:14:12.600 --> 00:14:14.260
will not let you have your way.

00:14:17.680 --> 00:14:18.660
Now,

00:14:19.200 --> 00:14:20.160
you

00:14:20.460 --> 00:14:21.980
and your son

00:14:22.010 --> 00:14:23.570
are both in my hands.

00:14:23.880 --> 00:14:25.680
You have no choice but to comply.

00:14:31.280 --> 00:14:32.880
My Li family

00:14:33.370 --> 00:14:35.760
only has martyrs who protect the state,

00:14:36.080 --> 00:14:37.880
not hostages who fear death.

00:14:37.880 --> 00:14:39.040
Well said!

00:14:39.040 --> 00:14:39.840
Good!

00:14:40.430 --> 00:14:41.870
Such eloquent words

00:14:41.900 --> 00:14:43.240
and noble integrity.

00:14:47.650 --> 00:14:49.390
But have you considered?

00:14:49.410 --> 00:14:50.450
What if

00:14:50.480 --> 00:14:52.340
I take the citizens of the Imperial City

00:14:52.340 --> 00:14:53.860
as hostages?

00:14:55.170 --> 00:14:56.490
What would you do then?

00:15:01.920 --> 00:15:03.120
What did you say?

00:15:16.440 --> 00:15:17.360
Are you saying

00:15:17.400 --> 00:15:19.910
Zhou Kui planted explosives
in the Imperial City?

00:15:19.910 --> 00:15:20.350
Yes.

00:15:22.530 --> 00:15:23.390
Your Highness,

00:15:23.570 --> 00:15:24.960
we should hurry to the palace.

00:15:24.960 --> 00:15:26.740
I'm really worried about Prince Yan.

00:15:26.740 --> 00:15:27.300
Alright.

00:15:28.210 --> 00:15:29.160
[Crown Prince's Mansion]

00:15:32.930 --> 00:15:34.450
By order of His Majesty,

00:15:34.600 --> 00:15:36.300
the Crown Prince and his party

00:15:36.330 --> 00:15:38.390
are to enter the palace immediately.

00:15:46.790 --> 00:15:47.800
Your Majesty,

00:15:49.150 --> 00:15:50.670
the life and death of

00:15:50.690 --> 00:15:52.350
tens of thousands of citizens

00:15:53.590 --> 00:15:55.250
in the Imperial City Qingzhou

00:15:56.090 --> 00:15:57.360
depends solely

00:15:57.380 --> 00:15:58.980
on Your Majesty's decision.

00:16:02.130 --> 00:16:03.130
Zhou Kui,

00:16:03.880 --> 00:16:05.740
what exactly are you trying to do?

00:16:07.060 --> 00:16:09.790
He planted explosives
around the Imperial City!

00:16:13.350 --> 00:16:14.350
Fu Wei.